message.en_US: Ok guys, we have the most balanced party composition possible.
Come on, guys! We can't lose to a solo player, start pulling your weight!
Wow, you actually won! Perhaps we should actually form a more balanced party.
This whole Triangle Strategy thing seems to be more of a meme than a viable party composition.
Everyone made fun of us for all choosing the same class, shows what they know!
It just goes to show that Tribladers are indeed the best class.
Let's all use \c[3]overclock\c[0], just like we practiced!
